The Updates of COVID -19 (as of 21 Feb) in Korea 

○ As of 09:00, 21 February, 2020, 74 additional cases are confirmed, which brings the total number of confirmed cases to 156. 139 confirmed cases are currently in isolation, 11,953 turned out to be negative, and 2,707 are being tested. 




