○ Of the 72 cases, 62 cases are identified in Daegu and Gyeongbuk province, and 12 cases from other area. Regardless of region, 44 cases are linked to the Shincheonji Church of Jesus, 14 cases including 1 fatal case are linked to Cheongdo Daenam hospital. And 15 cases are under investigation. 
 




